docs.lead_paragraph: ELAZER B. DICKEY, a revolutionary veteran, died in Monroe, Me., on the 8th inst., aged ninetythree years and three months. The services which Mr. DICKEY, in his vigorous youth rendered to his country, as well as the merits of his character in after life, demand more than a casual notice.
